  10 Nov 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> stepmania-9999.ebuild:
  Switched to virtual/jpeg

  02 Jul 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> stepmania-9999.ebuild,
  +files/stepmania-9999-libpng14.patch:
  Fixed build with libpng-1.4.

  18 Feb 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl>
  files/stepmania-9999-ffmpeg.patch:
  Updated ffmpeg patch.

  21 Jan 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> stepmania-9999.ebuild:
  Moved ESVN_* before inherit.

  07 Jan 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> stepmania-9999.ebuild,
  +files/stepmania-9999-ffmpeg.patch:
  Added patch to fix video playback with new versions of ffmpeg. Taken from
  http://www.stepmania.com/forums/showthread.php?t=21434

  07 Jan 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> stepmania-9999.ebuild,
  +files/stepmania-9999-datadir.patch, -files/stepmania-gcc43.patch,
  +metadata.xml:
  Replacing with a slightly modified version of the live ebuild from Gentoo
  bug #148787. Still needs some work, but is worlds apart from the old
  abomination.

  06 Mar 2009; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl>
  files/stepmania-gcc43.patch:
  Removed some cruft from patch.

  04 Mar 2009; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl>
  +files/stepmania-gcc43.patch, stepmania-9999.ebuild:
  Added GCC 4.3 patch.

  21 Jan 2009; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> stepmania-9999.ebuild:
  Added RDEPEND.

  21 Jan 2009; Piotr Szymaniak <lazy_bum@o2.pl> stepmania-9999.ebuild:
  Fixed some whitespace and unquoted variables.

